Name: git-hooks
Version: 0.0.3
Summary: Show useful git hooks
Home-page: https://github.com/juanpabloaj/git-hooks
Author: JuanPabloAJ
Author-email: jpabloaj@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: =========
        git-hooks
        =========
        
        Show useful hooks by language and hook name.
        
        Install
        =======
        
        ::
        
            pip install git-hooks
        
        Usage
        =====
        
        List hooks availables for some language
        
        ::
        
            git hooks node
        
        
        Show hook
        
        ::
        
            git hooks node pre-commit
        
        
        Install hook
        
        ::
        
            git hooks node pre-commit > .git/hooks
            chmod u+x .git/hooks/pre-commit
        
        Contribute
        ==========
        
        Add hooks to `githook/hooks` directory.
        
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7
